    "body": "During inference, we can only store mPostAct and do not store pre activation results. This PR fix an assertion error raised in this case. \r\n\r\n```\r\n    y1 = torch.empty(T * K, I, dtype=x.dtype, device=x.device)\r\n    \r\n    gemm_gated(\r\n        x,\r\n        w1.permute(1, 2, 0).permute(2, 1, 0),\r\n        activation=\"swiglu\",\r\n        cu_seqlens_m=expert_frequency_offset,\r\n        A_idx=x_gather_idx,\r\n        preact_out=None,\r\n        postact_out=y1,\r\n        store_preact=False\r\n    )\r\n```\r\n\r\nTest cases are passed in both Hopper and Blackwell GPUs. ",
    "created_at": "2026-03-03T07:16:44Z",
